    g_AzakaSettings.Loops := 5
Gui, ICScriptHub:Add, Text, x15 y+15, Ult. this many times:
Gui, ICScriptHub:Add, Edit, vAzaka_Loops x+5 w50, % g_AzakaSettings.Loops
